headline: Smartmatic Case Documents Show Some Fox News Hosts’ Drive to Help Trump
summary: Prominent Fox hosts privately sought to help President Trump’s efforts to overturn the results of the 2020 presidential election, according to newly unredacted documents in a lawsuit against Fox.
